title: Graco Travel System, Stroller, Extra Base Westminster
text: Graco Travel System, Stroller, & Extra Base (Westminster) Stroller in Baltimore, MD Originally Posted On: SpreadMyAd Additional Comments: Very gently used Graco Travel System and extra base Everything in this package is in extremely good and clean condition. The stroller itself was probably used less than ten times as we normally used the car seat carrier for trips to the store, etc. $60 Or Stroller, Car Seat, and 1 car seat base - $50 Extra Car seat base - $10 Car Seat Carrier - $25 - sold
